@host = http://localhost:8080
@examId = 1
@userId = 101

### (1) 특정 문항 조회: GET /api/exams/{examId}/questions/{idx}
GET {{host}}/api/exams/{{examId}}/questions/1
Accept: application/json

### (2) 정답 제출: POST /api/exams/{examId}/answers
# SubmitAnswerRequest 필드명은 프로젝트 DTO에 맞춰 조정하세요.
# (스키마에 맞춰 userId, questionId, answerText로 예시)
POST {{host}}/api/exams/{{examId}}/answers
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "questionId": 1002,
  "answerText": "서울"
}

### (3) 진행 현황: GET /api/exams/{examId}/progress
GET {{host}}/api/exams/{{examId}}/progress
Accept: application/json

### (4) 특정 유저 상세(컨트롤러 경로명은 students지만 실제론 user_id)
GET {{host}}/api/exams/{{examId}}/students/{{userId}}
Accept: application/json
